OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch has
OL,7,Ftold firms to focus on delivering for
OL,8,Fcustomers rather than "activism or
OL,9,Fpolitical causes".
OL,11,FShe said there was a "creeping ` and
OL,12,Fcounter-productive ` politicisation"
OL,13,Fof business.
OL,15,FMs Badenoch said some firms' well-
OL,16,Fmeaning "equality, diversity and
OL,17,Finclusion" initiatives "divide, rather
OL,18,Fthan unify".
