OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FThe Business Secretary was speaking in
OL,7,Fsupport of a research programme by the
OL,8,FPolicy Exchange think tank on the
OL,9,Fissue.
OL,11,FA Deltapoll survey for the think tank
OL,12,Ffound 50% of people thought businesses
OL,13,Fhad become "too concerned with taking
OL,14,Fpolitical positions on contested
OL,15,Fissues", with 14% disagreeing ` the
OL,16,Fremainder either did not agree or
OL,17,Fdisagree, or did not know.
