OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FThe polling indicated that 75% of
OL,7,Fpeople believe that companies should
OL,8,Fhire on merit, regardless of race or
OL,9,Fgender, instead of seeking to create a
OL,10,Fdiverse team.
OL,12,FThe centre-right think tank's project
OL,13,Fwill "methodically document and
OL,14,Faddress the role and influence of
OL,15,Fsocial and ideological considerations
OL,16,Fon contemporary business",
OL,17,Fparticularly "at the expense of
OL,18,Fshareholder and wider society
OL,19,Finterests".
