OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FPolicy Exchange highlighted examples
OL,7,Fsuch as the debanking row, ice cream
OL,8,Fbrand Ben & Jerry's criticism of the
OL,9,FGovernment over asylum policies and
OL,10,Fcoffee chain Costa's mural showing a
OL,11,Ftransgender person with mastectomy
OL,12,Fscars sipping a drink on one of its
OL,13,Fexpress vans.
OL,15,FMs Badenoch said: "Policy Exchange's
OL,16,Ffindings confirm what I know to be
OL,17,Ftrue from talking to people who run
OL,18,Fbusinesses, work in them, and buy from
OL,19,Fthem.
