OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,F"The public want the focus of business
OL,7,Fto be on delivering great products and
OL,8,Fservices, not activism or political
OL,9,Fcauses ` which repel as many people as
OL,10,Fthey attract.
OL,12,F"Overwhelmingly, people want companies
OL,13,Fto recruit on merit, selecting the
OL,14,Fbest person for the job without regard
OL,15,Fto race or gender, rather than social
OL,16,Fengineering to create 'diverse teams'."
