OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FEarlier this year, an independent
OL,7,Fpanel appointed by Ms Badenoch found
OL,8,Fbusinesses are implementing diversity
OL,9,Fand inclusion initiatives without an
OL,10,Fevidence base.
OL,12,FMs Badenoch said: "As the recent
OL,13,FInclusion at Work Panel showed, many
OL,14,Fwell-meaning 'equality, diversity and
OL,15,Finclusion' initiatives divide rather
OL,16,Fthan unify, and undermine
OL,17,Forganisational goals.
OL,19,F"They are based on speculative and
OL,20,Fcontested theories with limited
OL,21,Fevidence of impact.
