OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,F"Policy Exchange's programme is a
OL,7,Ftimely and welcome contribution to
OL,8,Fdocument the creeping ` and counter-
OL,9,Fproductive ` politicisation of our
OL,10,Fbusiness environment.
OL,12,F"I am committed to working with
OL,13,Fbusinesses on effective ways to foster
OL,14,Feconomic growth, and also on this
OL,15,FGovernment's Inclusive Britain goals `
OL,16,Fsmarter ways to achieve true equality
OL,17,Fof opportunity."
