OL,3,CBadenoch tells firms to quit political
OL,4,Cactivism and focus on the business
OL,6,FPolicy Exchange senior research fellow
OL,7,FLara Brown said: "Customers do not
OL,8,Fbelieve that businesses need to
OL,9,Fdemonstrate commitment to progressive
OL,10,Fprinciples and do not make spending
OL,11,Fdecisions based on the political
OL,12,Fstatements of retailers.
OL,14,F"Employees are also negatively
OL,15,Faffected by the politicisation of
OL,16,Fbusiness, with many sceptical about
OL,17,Fworkplace schemes tailored towards
OL,18,Fequality, diversity and inclusion."
